descript.abstract: Dataset showing the distribution of electric transformers in Rwanda.
descript.purpose: The dataset shows the distribution of transformers in Rwanda. It contains the following attributes: HSV (High Side Voltage), Capacity, Serial Number, Responsible Electrogaz Station, General remarks. The dataset is not complete and contains only transformers which are close or on powerlines built after 1988. No ground truth has been done.
